!&nbsp;[[Dental consonant|Dentals]]&nbsp;
!&nbsp;[[Velar consonant|Velars]]&nbsp;
!&nbsp;[[labialized velar consonant|Labiovelars]]&nbsp;
!&nbsp;[[Palatovelar]]s&nbsp;
|-
!&nbsp;[[Voiceless consonant|Voiceless]]&nbsp;
